name: Black 2 (V)
Lore: 'TIE/ln assigned to pilot DS-61-2. Has 27 ''flames'' on cockpit, one for each Rebel kill. Control yoke has a holo of Mithels'' young son, Rejili.',
Text: 'May add 1 pilot. During your deploy phase, may take one Pride Of The Empire into hand from Reserve Deck; reshuffle. All Wings Report In and Organized Attack are canceled. While DS-61-2 piloting, immune to attrition < 5.',
